Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.41,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(316.43,936)\fad(400,400)}奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要說這話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,砍這種地方的樹 你想把房子壓垮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你要當伐木工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是戰爭 我在為戰爭訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 這威力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是塊頭大 在戰場上派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,準備吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 別扔小刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,扔盤子或者勺子不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,扔盤子你就願意？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 熊在入冬前必須吃很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你怎麼突然想起搞訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是為了保護這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡被燒光 好不容易重建了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也不想再遇到那種事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,古斯姆家的牛奶就是好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那男人可不是一般地會摸奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你這動作好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧算了吧 別跟戰士扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就甘心總是輸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸也是為了保護我們才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,重建了村子 和兩個美女共進美餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你們聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,進到林子裡就向前狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然後沿著河跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,羅塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也不要想 筆直往前跑就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥和媽媽都和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能行嗎 我扶你起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把我丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼說 你加把勁站起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 那邊還有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還有女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來 艾納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快點帶羅塔逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是快死的老太婆 這點力氣還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就能再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,艾納爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,羅塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他們怎麼不逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這姑娘還挺可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽死掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,羅塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,羅塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放開羅塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,饒不了你 居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.14,zhu,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,居然對哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙拿東西扎我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把這小子賣了換酒錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走 酒錢
